title: Tom Cosm - Ableton Live Dj Megaset Template.zip
description:
This is an Ableton Live DJ Template, set out to show the capabilities of Ableton Live, specifically how easy it can be to learn how to do your own real time remixes on the fly.

Basic and Advanced effects, chains, dummy clips - it's all in here.

This set also contains 12 top tunes, chopped up and ready to go.

Created by Ableton Live teacher and performer Tom Cosm.

A full hour high definition video and more information can be found at www.cosm.co.nz/DJ
